text: Romash Tasuki Dass (born December 15, 1988) is a former baseball player from Japan.https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.cgi?id=dass--001rom Dass played for the Nippon Ham Fighters in the Pacific League.https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.cgi?id=dass--001rom He was born to an Indian father and Japanese mother.https://www.excite.co.jp/news/article/TokyoSports_1458624/ ==References== Category:Living people Category:1988 births Category:Japanese baseball players Category:Japanese people of Indian descent
